urdu transliteration text:
sar pe ahle kisa ka hai sayaaapne nam fatema payaaap zeenat hai apne baba kiaur rakhti hai zainabi lehja
Ahlul Bayt,
@HujjatELC

saath dono jahan aate haijabhhi wo jamkaran aate haitujhse milne ko tere rauze parkhud imame zamaan aate hai
Imam Zamana (atfs) himself visits your holy shrine,
@HujjatELC

pohchi jo qum ajeeb manzar thakale parcham lage the har ek jaaaise matam kiya hai bhai kaqum ko tune banaya karbobala
There were black flags hung all around,
@HujjatELC

ilmo idraak aagahi dedemisle behlol zindagi dedenaqshbardaare za'ereen banaapne rauze pe naukri dede
Make us devoted pilgrims of yours,
@HujjatELC

shahzadi ko tere rauze parmotariz horahe hai sajde parehteraaman hai shukr ka sajdaaur wo bhi khuda ke kehne par
